  "text": "Based on the user preference, the appliances are primarily divided into two types: shiftable and non-shiftable [CITATION_1] . The non-shiftable appliances cannot be delayed but may be operated at reduced power. Rescheduling is applicable to the shiftable devices which can be delayed to relatively lower energy cost time periods. The delay preference for this type of appliances depends on user comfort. The shiftable appliances may also be operated at reduced power.",
